The course deals with public communication as a part of of communication culture. Attention is payed to the theory of speech and factors affecting the public communication.Objectives/eesmärkid:  To give the basic skills to evaluate personal communication skills, find solutions to the problems and for public communication.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  After the course the student:  -knows how to use the terms related to public communication; - knows the factors affecting public communication; -can design a speech according to the purpose; - can use the appropriate methods for designing the speech; -knows the essential skills of the public speaker; -is able to follow his own speaking style and develop it; - is able to find the relationship between public communication and professional success.
